Arduino Pin Connections

Motors via L298N:

IN1 → D5

IN2 → D4

IN3 → D8

IN4 → D12

ENA → D3 (PWM for speed)

ENB → D11 (PWM for speed)


Front Obstacle Sensor (HC-SR04, fixed):

Trig → D6

Echo → D7

VCC → 5V

GND → GND


Radar Sensor (HC-SR04 on servo):

Trig → D9

Echo → D10

VCC → 5V

GND → GND


Radar Servo:

Signal → D11 (PWM)

VCC → 5V

GND → GND


OLED Display (I2C 128x64):

SDA → A4

SCL → A5

VCC → 5V

GND → GND


Power:

2S Li-ion Battery (7.4V) → Arduino VIN and L298N VIN

GND → common ground for Arduino, L298N, sensors, and servo
